00:12:17,316 --> 00:12:18,776
was it's everybody else's fault.

265
00:12:18,916 --> 00:12:20,597
This isn't my fault, it's other people's fault.

266
00:12:20,617 --> 00:12:21,697
That's why I'm such a jerk.

267
00:12:22,497 --> 00:12:24,438
And the key to breaking that cycle

