276
00:12:45,882 --> 00:12:48,325
that this isn't a new Kratos.

277
00:12:48,785 --> 00:12:52,289
This is the same Kratos who's just a lot older.

278
00:12:52,590 --> 00:12:55,252
So that means he still has this monster inside of him.

