00:35:56,203 --> 00:35:57,345
while we were building the plane

870
00:35:57,385 --> 00:35:59,227
and also drawing the blueprints of the plane.

871
00:36:00,371 --> 00:36:01,211
as it was taking off.

872
00:36:01,231 --> 00:36:04,713
It was fantastic and incredibly, incredibly stressful.

873
00:36:05,333 --> 00:36:07,774
So as we're going closer, it starts to hit

874
00:36:08,214 --> 00:36:10,836
that I'm gonna have to play this thing live, right?

875
00:36:10,856 --> 00:36:12,536
And it's gonna be nine minutes.

876
00:36:13,117 --> 00:36:14,137
So I start rehearsing,

877
00:36:14,157 --> 00:36:16,918
and I'm gonna rehearse for like two months, right?

878
00:36:17,478 --> 00:36:19,299
And I think, and there's a bunch of members

879
00:36:19,359 --> 00:36:21,460
of the team here, so they'll probably agree with this,

880
00:36:21,520 --> 00:36:21,740
I hope.

881
00:36:23,301 --> 00:36:24,841
This is probably the greatest time for the team

882
00:36:24,941 --> 00:36:27,262
because I was basically playing for the team

883
00:36:27,482 --> 00:36:28,822
while they all shouted notes at me

