00:38:20,366 --> 00:38:22,307
And then we had a couple of rehearsals with the orchestra.

942
00:38:23,087 --> 00:38:25,628
But it was all leading up to the day of the show.

943
00:38:27,089 --> 00:38:31,191
And throughout all this time, I am constantly just in my head

