00:39:51,893 --> 00:39:53,094
What do you think people are going to say on Reddit?

975
00:39:53,675 --> 00:39:56,997
And I was like, you know, I hadn't gotten that specific in my neurosis to say,

976
00:39:57,037 --> 00:39:59,559
like, what is Reddit going to say? But I'm there now, dude. Thanks.

